2	//!
3	//! The shared parser (`parse_util`) reads each captured fixture into the crate's
4	//! own [`Graph`] model; re-serializing with [`graph_clean::dot::to_dot`] must
5	//! reproduce the original bytes exactly. This validates the payload-format spec
